Description:
Plenty of OPTIONS in sought after locale
Go to http://b.link/16donaxrdcorio for further information.
This home will suit owner occupiers, investors, and developers alike! Offering an allotment of 1114m2 (approx.) zoned Residential Growth Zone 2 (RGZ2) with no easements. Alternatively, there is plenty of room for a vegetable garden / chooks while still having short communities to both Geelong, Melbourne and the Surf Coast. A real find in the heart of Geelong's northern growth corridor in Corio.
This roomy three-bedroom home features polished floorboards, 9-foot ceilings, large kitchen & dining area. Formal lounge with gas heating, three extra-large bedrooms all with built in robes, sun-room and bathroom with separate shower and bath. As you step outside you are greeted with a well-established and expansive yard with plenty of scope for extensions or development! Alternately there is plenty of grassed areas to be used as a children's play area, or ideal for pets!
Easy access to both the Princess Highway/Melbourne Road and the Princess Freeway means just a 10-minute drive to Geelong's CBD and ideally located for Melbourne commuters. The home is located close to public transport.
Don't miss this opportunity to make your mark right here in Corio.

Calling all developers and investors alike.
Rarely does an opportunity like this come up on such a huge parcel of land so close to everything. This great character home on a huge 1445m2 (approx.) allotment and zoned Residential growth zone -Schedule 2 (RGZ2) lends itself to extension, renovation or development (STCA). This lovely character California Bungalow comes complete with 3 bedrooms, study, central bathroom, meals, kitchen area, separate lounge room with gas heating and a large timber lined rumpus room with polished timber floors for those large family get together or turn it into a recreation room. Conveniently located close to all major amenities including the Corio Village shopping centre, local schools, medical centres and with plenty of public transport available, this location is central to everything.

appointed ensuite and walk in robe
